    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Knives of various designs having a curved blade set transversely to the handle, used in leatherworking and other occupations. For such knives with a curved blade in the shape of a crescent moon, use "moon knives."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
